      WILLIAM ANDERSON ROSE
, Esq., M.P.; 



      WILLIAM LAWRENCE
, Esq.; Aldermen of the said City; RUSSELL GURNEY, Esq., Q.C., Recorder of the said City; WILLIAM FERNELEY ALLEN, Esq.; JOHN JOSEPH MECHI, Esq.; SILLS JOHN GIBBONS, Esq., Aldermen of the said City; 



